headline: Tandem Diabetes Care Announces Second Quarter 2025 Financial Results and Provides 2025 Annual Guidance
summary: SAN DIEGO, August 06, 2025--Tandem Diabetes Care, Inc. (Nasdaq: TNDM), a global insulin delivery and diabetes technology company, today reported its financial results for the quarter ended June 30, 2025 and provided full year 2025 guidance.
